NATION
  Show your country's economic and development overview.

SYNTAX
  nation [<cnum>]
  nati   [<cnum>]

DESCRIPTION
  Displays key statistics for your country:
    money     - treasury ($).  Negative means debt
    reserve   - military reserve (troops for enlist command)
    tech      - technology level.  Unlocks advanced units
    research  - research level.  Prerequisite for high tech
    education - education level.  Improves production
    happiness - happiness.  Affects civilian work rate

  Deities can view any country by passing its number.
  Players see only their own stats unless relations allow.

  Technology, research, education, and happiness grow each update
  based on what you produce in tech centers, research labs,
  libraries, and agribusiness sectors.

EXAMPLE
  nation                    view your own stats
  nation 3                  view country 3 (deity only)

